commitResults.messageTitle: Rename bot name from Duke to Owen
Add Response interface and DefaultResponse implementation
commitResults.messageBody: Response represents a formatted chatbot response message.

commitResults.messageTitle: Create Chatbot interface and make Owen implement it
commitResults.messageBody:
Chatbot interface is decoupled from main loop and user input /
output. To get a response from the Chatbot, a method must be
implemented and called to get the latest response.

commitResults.messageTitle: Add methods to shutdown Chatbot and check if it currently running
Add ability to parse commands and implement Echo and Exit commands
commitResults.messageBody:
As chatbot is immutable, parsing commands will return a new copy
of the chatbot with its internal state changed.

commitResults.messageTitle: Implement main loop that handles user input / output
Add Javadocs to Chatbot interface and Owen chatbot
Implement Add and List commands in Owen
commitResults.messageBody:
* Echo command is replaced by Add command
* Add command adds items to a list that Owen keeps track of
* List command lists out items that Owen is keeping track of

commitResults.messageTitle: Add general Task and TaskList to keep track of Tasks
Add ability to mark tasks as done in Owen
commitResults.messageBody:
Owen uses List of Strings to keep track of tasks. In order to make
Task management abstract, use a TaskList instead that allows adding
and marking of tasks as done.

commitResults.messageTitle: Make Task abstract and add support for todo, event, and deadline tasks
Make adding of tasks more verbose
Add Automated Text UI Testing
commitResults.messageBody: * Changed task status icon to use X
